Package org.opensextant.giscore.data

Class DocumentTypeRegistration

java.lang.Object
org.opensextant.giscore.data.DocumentTypeRegistration
public class DocumentTypeRegistration extends Object
Stores the registration information for a given pair of an input and output stream and a document type. Either the input or output stream can be missing, in which case that entry will be ignored for the purposes of the factory. This class is not used as a key, so there's no immediate reason to define hashCode or equals.

DRAND

    • checkArguments

      public void checkArguments(boolean input, Object[] arguments)
      Check the count and types of the arguments against the required types
      Parameters:
      input - true for input, false for output
      arguments - the arguments required for each argument, is it required? If required has fewer elements than types or arguments the remainder is treated as false. If a false element is found, any further true value is ignored, i.e. only leading arguments are considered required.
